 <li><strong>Problem</strong>: Federated schema has <code>washType: CodeDes=
cription!</code> (non-null). Legacy has <code>washType: CodeDescription</co=
de> (nullable). Any existing wash records with null <code>washType</code> w=
ill cause resolver errors.</li>
 <li><strong>Tasks</strong>: Confirm data quality in wash service. If nulls=
 exist, either backfill data or make field nullable in federated schema.</l=
i>
