1.6) is a net-new mutation =E2=80=94 not a replacement for <code>bulkUpdate=
Teams</code>. ADR 0.1.3 does NOT need to be resolved before this story.</li=
>
 <li><strong>Estimate</strong>: 2 pts</li>
