<h3 id=3D"MaterialsUI=E2=86=92FederatedGraphQLMigrationPlan-Epic1.2=E2=80=
=94WashUIMigration">Epic 1.2 =E2=80=94 Wash UI Migration</h3>
<blockquote>
 <p><strong>ADR dependencies</strong>: None. Can begin once Epic 1.1.4 (que=
ries) is deployed to dev. <strong>Phase 0 prerequisites</strong>: Stories 0=
.2.1 (cache config), 0.2.3 (file convention).</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>Story 1.2.1 =E2=80=94 Wash Detail Page: Migrate Read Queries</st=
rong></p>
<ul>
 <li><strong>Library</strong>: <code>spark-wash</code> Nx lib in <code>pdex=
-ui-react</code>.</li>
 <li><strong>Tasks</strong>:=20
  <ul>
   <li>Create <code>washFederatedQueries.ts</code> (this becomes the refere=
nce implementation for Story 0.2.3).</li>
