<p><strong>Story 2.5.2 =E2=80=94 Fix <code>SPARK_TrimFacility.approvedColor=
Rows</code> Regression</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li><strong>Problem</strong>: Federated schema has <code>approvedColorRowI=
ds: [String]</code> (raw IDs). Legacy has <code>approvedColorRows: [SPARK_T=
rimColorRow]</code> (resolved objects).</li>
 <li><strong>Fix</strong>: <code>spark-trim</code> subgraph resolves <code>=
approvedColorRows</code> by fetching <code>Color</code> entity stubs from <=
code>spark-color</code> via federation entity resolution. Gateway batches N=
+1 via <code>@BatchMapping</code>.</li>
