<h3 id=3D"MaterialsUI=E2=86=92FederatedGraphQLMigrationPlan-Epic2.10=E2=80=
=94HubUIMigration">Epic 2.10 =E2=80=94 Hub UI Migration</h3>
<blockquote>
 <p><strong>ADR dependencies</strong>: ADR 0.1.3 (mutations), ADR 0.1.9 (te=
ams field), ADR 0.1.7 (multi-hop fields), ADR 0.1.4 (createResourceLink). N=
o dependency on other domain UI migrations.</p>
 <p><strong>Key UI complexity</strong>: The Hub UI has two distinct sub-sys=
tems =E2=80=94 the <strong>BaseMaterial detail/edit pages</strong> (shared =
across all 30 material types) and the <strong>Material Template admin pages=
</strong> (template hierarchy, attribute configuration). Both must be migra=
ted. Paper/Wood/UserDefinedMaterial each have their own full page sets.</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>Story 2.10.1 =E2=80=94 Hub Detail Page: Migrate Read Queries for=
 <code>BaseMaterial</code></strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>Migrate <code>GET_HUB_MATERIAL_AND_TEMPLATE_PERMISSIONS</code> and <co=
de>GET_HUB_MATERIAL_BY_ID</code> to <code>plmClient</code>.</li>
 <li>Field renames: <code>humanId</code> =E2=86=92 <code>id</code>; <code>n=
ame</code> =E2=86=92 <code>description</code>; <code>files</code> =E2=86=92=
 <code>primaryAttachment</code>/<code>designAttachment</code>.</li>
 <li><code>BaseMaterialColorway.humanId</code> =E2=86=92 <code>id</code> (d=
epends on Story 2.9.1).</li>
 <li><code>composition.hubMaterial</code> and <code>composition.template</c=
ode> sub-fields (depends on Story 2.9.1).</li>
 <li><code>supplierInfo</code>, <code>recycledContent</code>, <code>product=
Type</code> fields (depends on Story 2.9.1).</li>
 <li>Missing: <code>teams</code>, <code>businessPartners</code>, <code>drop=
pedPartnerIds</code> =E2=80=94 depends on ADR 0.1.9 (Story 2.9.1).</li>
 <li>Missing: <code>developedBaseMaterials</code>, <code>connectedBoms</cod=
e>, <code>searchResourceLinks</code> =E2=80=94 depends on Story 2.9.4 (ADR =
0.1.7).</li>
 <li><strong>Depends on</strong>: Story 2.9.1, 0.2.1, 0.2.3.</li>
 <li><strong>Estimate</strong>: 8 pts</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Story 2.10.2 =E2=80=94 Hub Paper / Wood / UserDefinedMaterial Pa=
ges: Migrate</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>Migrate <code>GET_PAPER_BY_ID</code>, <code>GET_PAPER_ENUMS</code>, <c=
ode>ADD_PAPER</code>, <code>UPDATE_PAPER</code> to <code>plmClient</code>.<=
/li>
 <li>Migrate <code>GET_WOOD_BY_ID</code>, <code>GET_WOOD_ENUMS</code>, <cod=
e>ADD_WOOD</code>, <code>UPDATE_WOOD</code> to <code>plmClient</code>.</li>
 <li>Migrate <code>UserDefinedMaterialView</code>, <code>UserDefinedMateria=
lModify</code>, <code>UserDefinedMaterialNew</code> containers.</li>
