</ul>
<p><strong>Story 2.10.3 =E2=80=94 Hub Material Template Admin Pages: Migrat=
e</strong></p>
<ul>
 <li>Migrate <code>GET_TEMPLATE_DETAILS_FOR_FORM</code>, <code>GET_TEMPLATE=
_HIERARCHY</code>, <code>GET_TEMPLATE_BY_ID</code>, <code>ADD_MATERIAL_TEMP=
LATE</code>, <code>UPDATE_MATERIAL_TEMPLATE</code> to <code>plmClient</code=
>.</li>
 <li>Migrate <code>MaterialTypeEdit</code>, <code>MaterialTypeNew</code>, <=
code>MaterialTypeView</code>, <code>MaterialTypeForm</code> containers.</li=
>
 <li><strong>Depends on</strong>: Story 2.9.3.</li>
 <li><strong>Estimate</strong>: 8 pts</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Story 2.10.4 =E2=80=94 Hub Create / Edit Mutations: Migrate</str=
ong></p>
<ul>
 <li>Migrate <code>PARTIAL_UPDATE_HUB_MATERIAL</code>, <code>VALIDATE_MATER=
IAL_UNIQUENESS</code>, <code>BULK_MATERIAL_VALIDATE_UNIQUENESS</code>, <cod=
e>ADD_RELATIONSHIP</code>, <code>ADD_FAVORITE_MATERIAL_TYPES</code>, <code>=
CHANGE_MATERIAL_VIEW_SETTING</code> to <code>plmClient</code>.</li>
