<blockquote>
 <p><strong>Note</strong>: ~243 pts UI-only. ~331 pts backend gap-fill + AD=
Rs. Total ~574 pts across both tracks. <strong>Sequencing change</strong>: =
Hub moved from Phase 4 =E2=86=92 Phase 2 (no domain sequencing dependency =
=E2=80=94 <code>@key</code> entities already live). Cross-cutting UI migrat=
ions (<code>getMaterialByIdFromService</code>, <code>bulkUpdateTeams</code>=
, <code>createResourceLink</code>) moved from Phase 4 =E2=86=92 Epic 0.2. P=
hase 4 is now Search only. <strong>Hub complexity update</strong>: Hub is n=
ow correctly rated =F0=9F=94=B4 (same tier as Color/Trim/Fabric) =E2=80=94 =
dynamic template system (runtime hierarchy, unknown N types), Paper/Wood/UD=
M concrete sub-types, composition N+1, three two-hop Relationship service t=
raversals, cross-domain <code>createResourceLink</code> write-back, VMM sup=
plier N+1.</p>
</blockquote>
